<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.3.9">
<l>naṉṉeñcē namperumāṉ nāḷu miṉitamarum</l>
<l>aṉṉañcēr kāṉa laṇiyāli kaitoḻutu</l>
<l>muṉṉañcēr valviṉaikaḷ pōka mukilvaṇṇaṉ</l>
<l>poṉṉañcēr cēvaṭimēl pōtaṇiyap peṟṟōmē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Good heart, worshiping, hands [joined], in lovely Āli</l>
<l>With seashores where swans gather,</l>
<l rend="indent">where our lord ever dwells happily,</l>
<l>So that the harsh fate attached to the past departs,</l>
<l rend="indent">we obtained blossoms to wear</l>
<l>[That were] on the rosy feet with the beauty of gold</l>
<l rend="indent">of the cloud-colored one.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
